description: Eli Hunter"The Hammer"Ht: 5'7" WT: 150lbs Season W/L record (1-1)Sebastian Keys"The Tiger"Ht: 6'0" WT: 170lbsSeason W/L record (9-6) Hitting the mat for an epic bout for sexual domination, we have Eli "The Hammer" Hunter, challenging NK's own Sebastian "The Tiger" Keys. With a few years of wrestling as well as martial arts, The Hammer says he has what it takes to take the win and dominate in the sex round. The Tiger also has martial arts training, and being a veteran here on NK, he doesn't plan on going down without one hell of a fight. Will The Hammer keep his promise and relentlessly fuck his opponent without mercy? Or will he have no other choice but to submit and take it up the ass?
title: Eli "The Hammer" Hunter vs Sebastian "The Tiger" Keys
